1) Update the application and token details in settings.xml

refresh_offset - Offset time to call the refresh endpoint before token expire.(in seconds)
token_endpoint - token endpoint eg: https://localhost:9444/oauth2/token.
app_key - Consumerkey of the Application that has subscribed to sms api.
app_secret - Consumer Secret.
username - username of the user that communicates with the token endpoint to retrieve a token.
password - password of the user.
access_token - default access token.
refresh_token - referesh token
validity_period - validity period of the token (in seconds)
token_created_timestamp - token created timestamp (in milliseconds)

2) execute the jar.
java -jar -Dlog4j.configuration=file:conf/log4j.properties smsc-server-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar